  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t如题，秦刚可是我包弟亲自指挥亲自部署提拔起来的外交大将，劳累了大半辈子放松放松怎么了？<br/>\n<br/>\n再说慎海雄，广电局的地位应该不比外交部重要。而且他可是把情妇佟丽娅带出去玩，被人拍到坐实了，性质极其恶劣。反而中共还授意全网删帖封号，并且抓捕相关人等，甚至还帮助佟丽娅去加拿大🇨🇦打官司维权。<br/>\n<br/>\n突发奇想，丫丫的脸感觉和年轻时的媛神好像，莫非慎海雄真是替习畜守着藏娇的金屋？（貌似陈破空提出过这个说法）<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjhmMWQ1Mzc1NzJiYmY1ZjUxMDc2LmpwZz93aWR0aD04MjgmaGVpZ2h0PTc3Mw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f1d537572bbf5f51076.jpg?width=828&amp;height=773\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f1d537572bbf5f51076.jpg?width=828&amp;height=773\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/68f1d537572bbf5f51076.jpg?width=828&amp;height=773\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGE4NjAzODJkMTIyMWI0MjA2ZTZkLnBuZz93aWR0aD02ODAmaGVpZ2h0PTU3MQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da860382d1221b4206e6d.png?width=680&amp;height=571\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da860382d1221b4206e6d.png?width=680&amp;height=571\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/da860382d1221b4206e6d.png?width=680&amp;height=571\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
